title: Digits
alt: It's taken me 20 years to get over skyline tetris.
transcript:
[A guy is walking and Cueball is following him.]
Guy: The talk is in room 8224.
Cueball: Ooh, nice.
Guy: What?
Cueball: ...Sorry. Nothing.Great, now I'll spend the rest of my life noticing numbers that would make good 2048 combos.
